timeline.bodyText:
@kwart @jerrinot I think we need to add similar fail safe to release automation, I will work on it, please let me know if you see that redundant after this test case.

Update:
created https://github.com/hazelcast/hazelcast-pipeline-library/issues/119 on automation side. Thanks @kwart for the guidance.

